title: Ane Brun - Songs 2003-2013 - 2CD
description:
Brun was born in Norway and lives in Stockholm. She has recorded eight albums over the last ten years. Songs 2003-2013 is a confirmation of Brun's achievements as a songwriter. She isn't resting on her laurels, she is merely stating that she is here to stay.
